{"tid":2198441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張竹君: 我不是口罩專家 但唔好掂口罩外面係常識","createTime":"2020-09-11T10:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T15:47:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"041e5d23c63cc529647765275eb1c6cc2c0e3c51","tid":2198441,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:55:12.000Z","msg":"衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君今日（11日）在疫情記者會上，被追問對張宇人言論的回應，她先指自己不是口罩方面專家，著記者可以問感染控制專家；之後再被追問時指就口罩方面沒補充。其後有記者再問張，指張稱自己不是口罩專家，會否收回日前除口罩風險的言論，張竹君表示，「唔好掂口罩外面，或者掂之前之後洗手係普通常識，我諗大家戴口罩都知道」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/K7BE7AQASJDIVOX6LFR7XCATLE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FK7BE7AQASJDIVOX6LFR7XCATLE%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=1af2dc68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FK7BE7AQASJDIVOX6LFR7XCATLE%2F&h=a410a290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/K7BE7AQASJDIVOX6LFR7XCATLE/</a>"},{"pid":"efa3ca2e2716bd65bd188fb6d39e69c77f6fddd1","tid":2198441,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"good ball"},{"pid":"6f9099ad805b811ca02b22f8893f9147cffa2cf0","tid":2198441,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦 依家都接近0宗<br />\n幾時可以全民向口罩說不<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb7f700ccbc99c536a649d51bf34b5a37c147b0","tid":2198441,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316bad748c230fc19395fe50f749ecc0a6029719","tid":2198441,"u